Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Classes
  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Classes 
    Class and Description
    com.onlinepayments.domain.PaymentLinkOrderInput
    An object containing the details of the related payment input. All properties in paymentLinkOrder are deprecated. Use corresponding values as noted below: | Property | Replacement | | - | - | | merchantReference | references/merchantReference | | amount | order/amountOfMoney | | surchargeSpecificInput | order/surchargeSpecificInput |
    com.onlinepayments.domain.RedirectPaymentProduct809SpecificInput
    Deprecated, this is no longer used.
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    com.onlinepayments.domain.TokenEWallet.getAlias()
    This field is not used by any payment product An alias for the token. This can be used to visually represent the token.
    com.onlinepayments.domain.ShoppingCart.getAmountBreakdown()
    Use order.shipping.shippingCost for shipping cost. Other amounts are not used. Determines how the total amount is split into amount types
    com.onlinepayments.domain.PaymentOutput.getAmountPaid()
    Amount that has been paid. This is deprecated. Use acquiredAmount instead.
    com.onlinepayments.domain.CaptureOutput.getAmountPaid()
    Amount that has been paid. This is deprecated. Use acquiredAmount instead.
    com.onlinepayments.domain.APIError.getCode()
    Use errorCode instead. Error code
    com.onlinepayments.domain.FraudFields.getCustomerIpAddress()
    Use order.customer.device.ipAddress instead. The IP Address of the customer that is making the payment
    com.onlinepayments.domain.CreatePaymentLinkRequest.getDescription()
    A note related to the created payment link. Use paymentLinkSpecificInput/description instead.
    com.onlinepayments.domain.CreatePaymentLinkRequest.getExpirationDate()
    The date after which the payment link will not be usable to complete the payment. The date sent cannot be more than 6 months in the future or a past date. It must also contain the UTC offset. Use paymentLinkSpecificInput/expirationDate instead.
    com.onlinepayments.domain.AirlineFlightLeg.getFare()
    Use legFare instead. Fare of this leg
    com.onlinepayments.domain.AirlineData.getFlightDate()
    This field is not used by any payment product Date of the Flight Format: YYYYMMDD
    com.onlinepayments.domain.ExternalTokenLinked.getGTSComputedToken()
    Use the field ComputedToken instead.
    com.onlinepayments.domain.PaymentProductFieldTooltip.getImage()
    This field is not used by any payment product Relative URL that can be used to retrieve an image for the tooltip image.
    com.onlinepayments.domain.AirlineData.getIsETicket()
    Deprecated
    com.onlinepayments.domain.AirlineData.getIsThirdParty()
    This field is not used by any payment product * true - The payer is the ticket holder * false - The payer is not the ticket holder
    com.onlinepayments.domain.PaymentProductFieldDisplayHints.getLink()
    Deprecated

    com.onlinepayments.domain.CardPaymentMethodSpecificInput.getSkipAuthentication()
    Use threeDSecure.skipAuthentication instead. * true = 3D Secure authentication will be skipped for this transaction. This setting should be used when isRecurring is set to true and recurringPaymentSequenceIndicator is set to recurring. * false = 3D Secure authentication will not be skipped for this transaction. Note: This is only possible if your account in our system is setup for 3D Secure authentication and if your configuration in our system allows you to override it per transaction.
